XBMC Fargo "Addon" 
------------------
To import the data from XBMC to Fargo you need to copy the fargo folder to the XBMC web server, i.e.:

Windows - C:\Program Files\XBMC\addons\webinterface.default\
OpenElec - ~/usr/share/xbmc/addons/webinterface.default/
Raspbmc - /opt/xbmc-bcm/xbmc-bin/share/xbmc/addons/webinterface.default/
or 
Raspbmc - /home/pi/.upgrade/[build]/xbmc-bcm/xbmc-bin/share/xbmc/addons/webinterface.default/

Config Fargo "Addon" 
--------------------
Open the fargo.settings.js file and enter your Fargo web site URL.